    <item>
      <title>CATL与特斯拉合作开发快充电池，供应内华达州</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-25/catl-working-with-tesla-on-fast-charging-cells-supplying-nevada</link>
      <description><![CDATA[埃隆·马斯克 (Elon Musk) 旗下的汽车制造商力图捍卫其市场份额并推出一款售价低于 25,000 美元的电动汽车，当代新能源科技有限公司 (Contemporary Amperex Technology Co. Ltd.) 正在为特斯拉公司 (Tesla Inc.) 开发更快的充电电池。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-25/catl-working-with-tesla-on-fast-charging-cells-supplying-nevada</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 25 Mar 2024 07:20:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日产计划到 2027 年将销量增加 100 万辆</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-25/nissan-new-plan-targets-extra-1-million-car-sales-in-three-years</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日产汽车公司的目标是在三年内将汽车销量增加 100 万辆，这家日本汽车制造商寻求重获市场动力并提高盈利能力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-25/nissan-new-plan-targets-extra-1-million-car-sales-in-three-years</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 25 Mar 2024 06:00:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>奈拉下跌导致利润暴跌，MTN 推动金融科技业务量增长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-25/mtn-africa-s-biggest-wireless-carrier-increases-fintech-volumes</link>
      <description><![CDATA[MTN Group Ltd. 表示，去年金融科技交易量增加了三分之一，尽管这家非洲最大的移动运营商报告称，由于尼日利亚奈拉贬值，利润出现了至少 30 年来的最大跌幅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-25/mtn-africa-s-biggest-wireless-carrier-increases-fintech-volumes</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 25 Mar 2024 05:50:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>比亚迪大幅降价，迎战电动汽车落后者丰田和大众</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-25/byd-takes-on-ev-laggards-toyota-vw-with-steep-china-price-cuts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[比亚迪公司并不满足于取代特斯拉公司成为全球最畅销的电动汽车制造商，它已将目光投向了吸引客户远离丰田汽车公司和大众汽车公司等公司，这是迄今为止最激进的一轮折扣活动之一在中国惨烈的价格战中。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-25/byd-takes-on-ev-laggards-toyota-vw-with-steep-china-price-cuts</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 25 Mar 2024 01:17:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
